de.tub.pes.syscir.sc_model

Class SCProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tub.pes.syscir.sc_model.SCProcess

  • public class SCProcess
extends java.lang.Object
    this class represents a SCProcess it has a Link to a SCFunction, a List of Events on which this process is sensitive for and en enumSet of Modifiers theirs also a nam, which ist usualy equal to the function-name an a Type, for example SCThread, SCMethod
    Author:
    Florian
